room_title: Escape room "Chef Gordonio Ramzini’s Culinary Academy" by Fantasy Escapes in Tampa
room_description:
Today is your last day at Chef Gordonio Ramzini’s Culinary Academy. It’s been a long and grueling session but Chef has been quite impressed with your work so far. You have only one more task to perform to graduate.
Your final exam consists of a series of tasks which will enable you to figure out today’s menu and you MUST complete it within an hour. Please remember there are no food or drinks in the classroom during exam time. So if you are ready, go ahead and put your apron on and get ready to have some fun.
